Edition:
Quote:  [The Hokitika newsboy put a newspaper] into my hand. `How much?' I asked `Ay-a tizzy.' Understanding this more familiar term, I gave him a shilling. [Is Dilke merely advertising his generosity]
Notes:  [see snapper]

